    "请先设置每日热量与营养目标，「今天」页即可查看每日摄入进度。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Set your daily calorie and nutrition goals first; then the Today tab will show your daily intake progress."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "请先设置每日热量与营养目标，「今天」页即可查看每日摄入进度。"
