    "仅在识别时，图片或文字会发送至所配置的 API endpoint；除此之外，App 不向任何地方发送数据。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Only during recognition are images or text sent to the configured API endpoint; otherwise the app sends no data anywhere."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "仅在识别时，图片或文字会发送至所配置的 API endpoint；除此之外，App 不向任何地方发送数据。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "责任边界": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Boundaries of responsibility"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "责任边界"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "若所配置的 endpoint 为第三方服务（OpenAI / 中转站 / 代理），图片将离开本机并按该服务的条款处理——相关信任与责任取决于对 endpoint 的选择。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "If the configured endpoint is a third-party service (OpenAI / relay / proxy), images leave the device and are handled under that service's terms — the trust and responsibility depend on your choice of endpoint."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "若所配置的 endpoint 为第三方服务（OpenAI / 中转站 / 代理），图片将离开本机并按该服务的条款处理——相关信任与责任取决于对 endpoint 的选择。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "若需做到「绝不外流」，请将 endpoint 配置为本地模型（如 Ollama）。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "For data that “never leaves the device,” configure the endpoint as a local model (e.g. Ollama)."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "若需做到「绝不外流」，请将 endpoint 配置为本地模型（如 Ollama）。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
